    <ele>335</ele>
    <name>🛏️ NIGHT 1 — Portomarín</name>
    <desc>Km 23.5 · Arrived 18:36 · 32,703 steps · Moving pace 12.7 min/km · Only 6% rest — Town rebuilt stone by stone after the 1960s dam flood.</desc>
