    <desc>Km 77.9 · Arrived 19:05 · 39,368 steps · LONGEST DAY (28.3 km, 9.5h) · 27% rest · Restored 12th-century pilgrim hospital at the bridge.</desc>
    <sym>Lodge</sym>
    <type>Sleep</type>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="42.929" lon="-8.161">
    <ele>387</ele>
    <name>🧀 Arzúa</name>
    <desc>Km 81 — Cheese capital (Queso de Arzúa-Ulloa DOP). Where the Camino del Norte joins.</desc>
